These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, scientific, family, epic, western, sports, action
The people have 7 different jobs:  social-worker, entrepreneur, coach, scientist, dancer, security-guard, journalist
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daffodil, sunflower, tulip, amaryllis, rose, orchid
There are 7 different favourite colors: apricot, black, aquamarine, fuchsia, grey, purple, orange
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 2. the scientist is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 5. the journalist is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the security-guard##1
 7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 9. the coach is on the far right##1
10. the coach is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
11. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
12. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
13. the dancer is in the middle##1
14. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
15. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
16. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
17. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
18. the coach is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
19. the person who likes aquamarine is in the middle##1
20. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
21. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Movie-Genre      | family    | crime     | action  | sports   | epic | western      | scientific          |
| Job   | journalist    | scientist   | security-guard  | dancer       | social-worker  | entrepreneur      | coach     |
| Flower         | zinnia | daffodil | amaryllis | rose | sunflower   | tulip     | orchid |
| Color     | orange      | purple   | apricot   | aquamarine  | fuchsia  | grey | black       |

